question: Which café is on the path towards Suzanne Kramer, Denver, CO within a 30 kilometers radius from Children's Hospital Colorado at Parker Adventist Hospital, Emergency Care, Parker, Parker, CO?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-104.769926 39.547935)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-104.977037 39.765773)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-104.769926 39.547935)',4326)::geography, 30000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-104.769926 39.547935)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
